Package: peity
Type: Package
Title: Inline Charts for R
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Samuel", "Macêdo", email = "svm.macedo@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("John", "Coene", email = "jcoenep@gmail.com", role = "aut")
    )
Maintainer: Samuel Macêdo <svm.macedo@gmail.com>
Description: Easily converts an element's content into a svg mini pie, donut, line or bar chart.
     Peity is a wrapper around peity.js and it is compatible with any browser that supports
     svg: Chrome, Firefox, IE9+, Opera, Safari.
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/samuelmacedo83/peity
BugReports: https://github.com/samuelmacedo83/peity/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 3.6)
Imports: 
    htmltools,
    htmlwidgets
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Suggests: 
    testthat
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
